prefs-help-gender:
tina kanamuhan a setin ku mapili’ay langat-pisinga’an.
sisetyimo apisaungay namapili’ay nu misu a sasakawawen mitakus tisuwan, anu sasukamu tu tawan mapatahkal tisuwan sa apisaungay tu matatungus a ngangan.
tina cesyun apabinawlan.
prefs-help-variant: maydih kisu sapaazih tina kakacawan a lacul kalukamu saca sasuala tu sulit nu kamu.
tog-oldsig: nu misuay ayzaay a sulitan a ngangan:
tog-fancysig: sulitan a ngangan mahiza ku Wikitext kamu (caay lunuk misanga’ masasiket)
prefs-help-signature: i sasukamu kasabelih buhci tu kamu kanca pisaungay "<nowiki>~~~~</nowiki>" pangangan, bkya tatebanan nu nisulitan amaliyaw tu sulitan nu ngangan atu tuki.
badsig:
mungangaw a saayaway sulitan a ngangan.
pikinsa HTML aazihen-paya.
badsiglength:
sulitan a ngangan nu misu mangaleb tanaya’.
kya tanaya’ sa amana mangasiw $1 {{PLURAL:$1|tatebanan nu nisulitan.}}
prefs-help-email:
imyiyo(email) puenengan ku mipili’ sasulitan langat-pisinga’an.
nika i miliyaw patizeng mima sa matineng pisaungay，hakay kisu kalamapawan tu mima.
prefs-help-email-required: imyiyo(email) puenengan manakanca suliten naca kasacacay.
prefs-help-email-others:
hakay kapah kisu mipili’ zuma misaungayay micaliw imyiyo(email) nu misu, misaungayay kasabelih saca  sasukamu kasabelih a siket masukazih tisuwan.
imyiyo(email) puenengan nu misu caay pabeli’ tu zuma amitakus tisuwanay a misaungayay.
noemailprefs: i numisuay a setin tu kanamuhan misetin imyiyo(email) puenengan, kya kapah kisu pisaungay uyniyay sasahicaan.
emailnotauthenticated: imyiyo(email) puenengan mu misu caay henay malucek, cayhenay patigami kisu isasa’ay a sasahicaan a imyiyo(email).
emailauthenticated: imyiyo(email) puenengan nu misu malucek tu i $2 $3.
allowemail: miwawah namakay zuma misaungayay a tigami patakus kungneng
tog-ccmeonemails: anu patigami kaku tu zuma misaungayay, patigami cacay mikilulay-cudad tu takuwan
tog-enotifwatchlistpages: anu miazihay a piazihan tu sulit a kasabelih saca tangan nu maku izaw ku sumad sa, pabahel imyiyo(email) patakus takuwan.
tog-enotifusertalkpages: anu sasukamu kasabelih nu maku masumad, pabahel imyiyo(email) patakus kaku
tog-enotifminoredits: anu kasabelih atu tangan izaw ku mikilulay asumad, pabahel imyiyo(email) patakus takuwan
tog-enotifrevealaddr: ilabu nu patakusay a tigami paazih imyiyo(email) puenengan
